title: CI/CD Pipeline - Deploy to Production

participant Developer as Dev
participant GitHub as GH
participant CI Runner as CI
participant Docker Registry as Reg
participant Kubernetes as K8s
participant Slack as Slack

Dev->>GH: git push origin main
GH->>CI: Webhook: push event (sha: a1b2c3)
note over CI: Spin up build environment
CI->>GH: Clone repo @ a1b2c3
GH-->>CI: Source code
CI->>CI: npm install
CI->>CI: npm run lint
CI->>CI: npm run test (142 tests)
note right of CI: All tests passed (34s)
CI->>CI: docker build -t app:a1b2c3
CI->>Reg: docker push app:a1b2c3
Reg-->>CI: Push complete (cache hit 4/6 layers)
CI->>K8s: kubectl set image deploy/app app:a1b2c3
K8s->>K8s: Rolling update (3 replicas)
note over K8s: Replace pods one-by-one
K8s-->>CI: Rollout complete
CI->>K8s: Run smoke tests /healthz
K8s-->>CI: 200 OK { status: healthy }
CI->>GH: POST commit status: success
CI->>Slack: Deploy succeeded: app@a1b2c3
Slack-->>Dev: #deploys: app deployed to prod
